  "title": "Community Care Associate| Community Hospital",
  "description": "<ul><li>Monitor vital sign</li><li>Assist to change bed linen and maintaing personal hygiene</li><li>Transfer, position patient in need</li><li>Ensure holistic care for elderly health, comfort and security</li><li>Deliver professional nursing care tailored to geriatric needs</li><li>Plan and implement meaningful activities for geriatric</li><li>Maintain accurate Individual Care Plans with timely updates and documentation</li><li>Assist with activities of daily living</li><li>Collaborate with caregivers and volunteers in elderly care best practic es</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min GCE O Level or equivalent</li><li>Min 2 years Singapore working experience in geriatric care</li><li>ITE Certificate in Home Care or Healthcare related certificate</li><li>Working hours: 3 shifts</li></ul><p>Check out Aber Care website for more details.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants may email your updated resume to career@abercare.sg.</p><p><br /></p><p>Abercare.sg | EA License No. 18C9070 | KOH SU WEN, CLARISSA| Registration No. R24119504</p>",
